data.description: Coastal  buildable waterfront lot  located on a cul-de-sac.  Excellent location on Mystic Island with short easy access to the Great Bay with no bridges to go under.   Enjoy all of the amenities that the Lagoon Life has to offer including boating, fishing, crabbing, the list goes on.   Convenient to all area shopping, restaurants, recreation, transportation GSP Exits 58 .  Conveniently located between Atlantic City and LBI and the best part are the views from this lot.  Views of the Great Bay and 7 bridges.  Don't pass this one by.......
